{"id": "1438673112488218644", "channel_id": "1438536875706028033", "type": 19, "author_id": "195401302145105920", "author_name": "jollysquire", "author_bot": false, "content": "right now, you have kind of a chill week of no decision to be made (unless you want OE Tawil). \n\nStarting on 17th, there will be daily reruns of Arc 2 characters, once a day for a week and it repeats 3 times after that (4 weeks of reruns). So you also have some time decide who exactly you want even after reruns start.\n\nAll that being said, for recommendations it's kinda just up to you on who you like to play, everyone from Arc 2 prefers E3 (excluding GDoll she just wants E1) but OE is always better, but is a high investment. If you are considering to OE someone I would say it's on GDoll, Clem, Castor or Pollux, but it's you account so do whoever.\n\nPersonally I would pull on Pickman or Pollux at all but it's your account 🙂", "timestamp": "2025-11-13T23:33:19.271000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-11-13T23:33:51.290000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["316600367892791296"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1438536875706028033", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1438536875706028033", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Pulls advice", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747463379390545"]}
